The '''Kyrouaquian High Council''' was the ruling body of the planet [[Kyrouac]]. They were approached by a diplomatic party from the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel Alliance]] during the height of the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]]. Some members wished to join the Rebels, whereas others feared retribution from the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]]. No decision was ever made, however, as one member of the council betrayed the Rebels to the Empire, and [[Star Destroyer/Legends|Star Destroyer]] came to the planet, unloading [[Stormtrooper/Legends|stormtroopers]] secretly by delivering them onto the planet in cargo ships. A young man by the name of [[CSL Danenberger]] informed the diplomats, and they promptly left the planet.

